Maintainer: Brandon Kramer <brandonleekramer@gmail.com>
Description: The tidyorgs package provides easy-to-use functions that 
      help standardize messy text data for organizational analysis. More specifically, 
      the functions standardize organizations across the academic, business, government 
      and nonprofit sectors. The package is intended to support linkage across multiple 
      datasets, bibliometric analysis, and sector classification for economic and policy analysis. 
